<p class="ql-align-center">7月31日下午6时20分许</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两名女生悄悄来到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">宜都市公安局陆城派出所</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">给值班民警送来自制冰粉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">二人将冰粉放到值班室门口后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">快速离去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“逃离”的样子极其可爱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><iframe width="500" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" border="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="//tv.sohu.com/s/sohuplayer/iplay.html?bid=208154903&amp;vars=%5B%5B%22showRecommend%22%2C0%5D%5D&amp;disablePlaylist=true&amp;mute=1&amp;autoplay=false"></iframe></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">民警发现篮子里除了自制冰粉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还附有花和小纸条</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">上面写着：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“盆、杯子、篮子，我明天来拿</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你们辛苦啦”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200804/962e29ac9fbc41c3a6712346f369ae83.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此视频一发出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">网友纷纷表示：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两个女孩子好有爱呀~</p>
