<p class="ql-align-center">昨日，民警联系上送冰粉的小姐姐</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对她们表示了感谢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小姐姐说自己是高中生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">曾经受过民警帮助</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天气热了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">便自己在家做了冰粉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">约朋友一同送来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">炎炎夏日</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两位小姐姐的举动</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">给民警带来一丝清凉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">给两位善良有爱的小姐姐</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">点个赞吧！</p>
